<title>
What is TE-Code?
</title>
<body>
<p>
TE-Code is a collection of Open Source Software available under the
revised <a
href="http://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.php">BSD
License</a>.  The collection is divided up into categories which
address some recurring problems I have seen in delivering software
over the past 10 years.
</p>
<p>
The library contains the following packages which are available
independently for various technologies.
